<i>noun</i>: 솔질 [솔ː질], 빗질 [빋찔] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>솔질 [솔ː질]</dt><br>
<dd>brushing</dd><br>
<dd>솔로 먼지 등을 털거나 닦는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of brushing or wiping off dust, etc., with a brush.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>빗질 [빋찔]</dt><br>
<dd>combing; brushing</dd><br>
<dd>머리카락이나 털 등을 빗으로 빗는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of arranging the hair, etc. with a comb or hairbrush.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>